SettingsPropertyCollection Class

In this Article

Contains a collection of SettingsProperty objects.

Syntax

Remarks

The SettingsPropertyCollection collection contains a collection of SettingsProperty objects. A SettingsProperty object is used internally as the class that represents metadata about an individual configuration property.
